{"tid":687681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嫌等太耐閃人 代理反鬧客「無錢唔好扮有錢」幾球買樓俾人問候","createTime":"2018-06-02T12:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T17:45:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfe571487f1bb6a9c165637167072c714a88621","tid":687681,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"恒地（012）大角嘴劏房盤利奧坊．凱岸今日首度開放示位，予公眾參觀，並於明日起收票，發展商稱預計最快下周末開售。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時許，記者在售樓廠現場所見，有長人龍等候睇示範單位，各年齡層都有，當中不乏情侶檔。本身居住在南區竹睇樓客張太太認為，樓盤位置近地鐵站及所屬區份好，所以感興趣，打算買入1個1房單位作投資用，還透露自己手持多個物業收租用。被問到會否擔心樓價跌及加息等，她指「樓市跌就唔好放，守住佢！就實得架啦，最緊要有錢守住。」<br />\n<br />\n期後，現場突然起混亂，多名代理叫囂，並圍着一對疑似夫婦睇樓客，幸有保安出手護着該對夫婦離去，不過仍有代理大罵「無錢就唔好扮有錢買樓」、「買樓唔洗排隊架」等表達不滿，其後向保安了解事件，相信是因為睇樓等候時間太長，所以失去耐性而離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269182&d=ALeaT3O9wnRj9vO2gfOxf%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=07740923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269182&h=763ae50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269182</a><br />\n<br />\n香港現象，俾aa屌老母"},{"pid":"abb5794a353186e5a36c87e49f510cb24ff5b79d","tid":687681,"uid":176366,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d97d6d5132893e8672a1f5d2051f8a9b7ae50ff","tid":687681,"uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"abb5794a353186e5a36c87e49f510cb24ff5b79d","tid":687681,"uid":176366,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma